==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Countercurrent
<hw>Coun"ter*cur`rent</hw> <pr>(koun"t?r-k?r`-r<it>e</it>nt)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <def>Running in an opposite direction.</def>⟦br⟧
