==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Countercurrent
<hw>Coun"ter*cur`rent</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A current running in an
opposite direction to the main current.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Counterdraw</ent>⟦br⟧
